  "observations": [
    "Top-level surface is global search bar with type-grouped autocomplete (Datasets / Dashboards / Terms / People) — search is the primary entry point, not navigation",
    "Search results page uses filter chips (type, platform, env, tag, term, owner, domain) as the canonical facet UI",
    "Browse-path tree (platform → env → DB → schema → table) is offered as alternative-to-search for known-world discovery",
    "Dataset detail uses tabbed layout by concern (Schema / Documentation / Lineage / Properties / Queries / Stats / Validation / Operations / Access) — each tab is a separate facet of the same URN",
    "Hero displays composite identity: name + platform icon + environment badge (PROD/DEV) + breadcrumb path + health badges (deprecated / incident / stale)",
    "Schema tab is a nested-tree (column → nested struct) where each row carries its own tags / terms / business-owner inline — column is a first-class metadata target",
    "Lineage tab is a graph-canvas with current entity centered, upstream-left / downstream-right, typed icons per node kind",
    "Column-level lineage is progressive disclosure: click column → highlights path through systems",
    "Lineage filters (depth, hop count, type, time range) live as graph-canvas controls, not as a separate page",
    "Glossary uses hierarchical taxonomy (Term Group → Term → child terms) with approval workflow (Proposal → Approve / Reject) requiring curator role",
    "Domain pages aggregate assets by business area with owner team highlighted as primary metadata",
    "Tags are lightweight polymorphic — same tag attaches to dataset, column, dashboard, term",
    "Ownership is typed (Technical / Business / Steward / Producer / Consumer) — multi-owner-by-role rather than single owner field",
    "Sibling links surface same-logical-entity across platforms as a horizontal pill row on hero",
    "Posts/Announcements pinned to home + entity pages — embedded blog as platform-team broadcast surface",
    "Health badges aggregate multiple aspects (deprecation + incident + freshness) into single hero indicator",
    "Stats tab shows time-series for row count / null % / distinct values per column — trends, not snapshots",
    "Validation tab shows pass/fail history of assertions as timeline — assertion is itself an entity with history",
    "Search ranking exposed as relevance signal via PageRank-like score from lineage + usage stats — usage is first-class authority",
    "Ingestion has dual surface: YAML recipe editor in UI + CLI for CI — same model, two materializations",
    "Permissions are policy-based with resource-level conditions (filter by domain/platform/tag) rather than flat role checks",
    "Actions framework is event-condition-action — Slack-on-incident, auto-tag-PII, auto-deprecate-90d-unused — declarative reactive rules",
    "Embedded analytics widgets ('Most queried tables', 'Top dashboards', 'Datasets with broken upstream') sit on home as cross-aggregate dashboard",
    "URN is the canonical identity surface — visible on entity pages, copyable, used for cross-platform referencing",
    "Aspects-as-facets pattern: same entity surfaces different metadata bundles per tab; aspects compose rather than inherit",
    "Deprecation requires confirmation form with reason — irreversibility-high marker on destructive metadata transitions",
    "Approval of glossary term is one-click for curator but has audit-trail implication (irreversibility-high)"
  ]
}